</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Pubic simfizini&#328; ultrases barlagy&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>pub sebtini anatomiki ta&yacute;dan takyk&nbsp;<b>g&ouml;rm&auml;ge&nbsp;</b>m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Simfizi&#328; uzalma derejesini kesgitlemek, eltmegi&#328; usulyny
sa&yacute;lamakda m&ouml;h&uuml;m &ouml;l&ccedil;egdir.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;anak s&uuml;&#328;klerini&#328; rentgen &#351;&ouml;hlesi&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>dogrumdan
so&#328;ky d&ouml;w&uuml;rde amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar, rentgen
&#351;ekili&nbsp;<b>d&uuml;w&uuml;n s&uuml;&#328;klerini&#328;&nbsp;</b>arasyndaky
aralygy kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r, biri-birine baglylykda gapdala we
&yacute;okary / a&#351;ak s&uuml;&yacute;&#351;melerini
g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Magnit-rezonans tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&ccedil;aga
doglandan so&#328; a&yacute;allarda &yacute;erine &yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r
we simfizi&#328; we &ccedil;anak s&uuml;&#328;klerini&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yna jikme-jik baha berm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
