color:black'>Agyry sindromyny a&yacute;yrmak &yacute;a-da azaltmak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;aga doglanda simfizi&#328; &yacute;arylmagyny&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Simfizit bilen agyr
agyry sindromy bilen g&ouml;wreli a&yacute;al d&uuml;&#351;ekde dyn&ccedil;
almaly.&nbsp;Uzak durmak &yacute;a-da k&ouml;p &yacute;&ouml;remek, bir
a&yacute;agy&#328;yza egilmek, basgan&ccedil;aklara &ccedil;ykmak &yacute;a-da
a&yacute;akly oturmak maslahat berilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;I&yacute;mitde
kalsi&yacute; ba&yacute; s&uuml;&yacute;t &ouml;n&uuml;mlerine (pe&yacute;nir,
kottej, s&uuml;&yacute;t we &#351;.m.) ileri tutulmalydyr, un
&ouml;n&uuml;mlerinden, &yacute;agly i&yacute;mitlerden ga&ccedil;a durmaga
synany&#351;y&#328;, agramy &yacute;okarlanmagyna, k&ouml;pelmegine seb&auml;p
bol&yacute;ar &ccedil;anaklyk halkadaky &yacute;&uuml;k we netijede agyry
sindromyny&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy.&nbsp;&Ccedil;anak halkasyndaky
&yacute;&uuml;ki azaltmak &uuml;&ccedil;in bint ge&yacute;mek maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r (s&uuml;&#328;kleri&#328; a&#351;a
b&ouml;l&uuml;nmegini&#328; we s&uuml;&yacute;&#351;megini&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni al&yacute;an berk bandaj).&nbsp;&Ccedil;anak muskullaryny,
a&#351;aky arka we bud my&#351;salaryny g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lendirmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;rite gimnastika toplumy
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
