</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y
dermanlary&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>ulanmak&nbsp;&ouml;n&uuml;m&ccedil;iligi
azaldyp, &ccedil;i&#351;iriji ara&ccedil;ylary&#328; i&#351;je&#328;ligini
peseldip biler, &#351;e&yacute;le hem reseptorlary&#328; agyry
du&yacute;gurlygyny&#328; &ccedil;&auml;gini &yacute;okarlandyryp biler.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
