14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Simfizi&#328; 1 sm
&yacute;a-da ondanam k&ouml;p gabat gelmezligi, sezary&yacute;a keselini&#328;
