<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aga doglandan
so&#328;, 1 sm-den gowrak d&uuml;w&uuml;n&ccedil;egi&#328;
artikul&yacute;asi&yacute;asyna la&yacute;yk gelme&yacute;&auml;n
a&yacute;allara, &ccedil;anaklary berk saramak we so&#328;undan bint
ge&yacute;mek bilen 2-6 hepde &yacute;atmak maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&Ccedil;anak s&uuml;&#328;klerini belli bir
&yacute;agda&yacute;da saklamak &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;rite
korsetleri&#328; ulanylmagy seb&auml;pli, d&uuml;&#351;egi&#328; berk
dyn&ccedil; almagy 3-5 g&uuml;ne &ccedil;enli azal&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&#350;e&yacute;le
korsetleri 3-6 a&yacute; ge&yacute;mek maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

